{"tid":2279700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警長遭紅酒濺腳，怒扯女下屬頭髮，今判服務令","createTime":"2020-11-10T03:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T10:56:02.000Z","uid":364767,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cc15e36349a62f60555b16b95d799943cc1074","tid":2279700,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/ZUGH33YM4NCK7PRRQC5BJ7LQ5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FZUGH33YM4NCK7PRRQC5BJ7LQ5Q%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=2adbbf5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FZUGH33YM4NCK7PRRQC5BJ7LQ5Q%2F&h=1ac036f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/ZUGH33YM4NCK7PRRQC5BJ7LQ5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍警署10名警員今年4月下班後違限聚令，一同食消夜為女同袍餞行，詎料其間發生警長打女警事件。涉案警長一再提出守行為了事但失敗，開審前改口承認普通襲擊罪，案情顯示女警當時向警長敬酒被拒，不但揶揄警長，紅酒更濺中他的白鞋，警長憤而扯女警頭髮10秒。裁判官水佳麗今判刑指被告因性格驕傲，對女警不留情，望被告對下屬多點包容，最終判處160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n現已停職的被告梁珏榮（40歲）被控於今年4月19日在元朗屏會街屏會中心外的行人路襲擊31歲女警蘇伶雅，辯方今求情指被告已停薪，願意接受服務令。<br />\n<br />\n「襲警」只判社會服務令。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家手足記住呢個案例"},{"pid":"426f369838ae2d4213adcae943ef6b9c0fb4bd1d","tid":2279700,"uid":72185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"doj上訴未?"},{"pid":"5bb044c9a538e9188e2ab315ee82f53bd5f1aa70","tid":2279700,"uid":125731,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法, 除非你係警察.......<br />\n同呢單野無抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6c71c3191a78b07e5c0956e11c3d4127d40d75","tid":2279700,"uid":225192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"社會寄生蟲犯法唔洗你教"},{"pid":"599bf2d4898caade15b53031bd5088a0b9000afb","tid":2279700,"uid":265925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci